<h2 class="tut-h2-pad" id="з•ЮзїПзљСзїЬ">з•ЮзїПзљСзїЬ
  <a href="/tutorials/machine-learning/torch/4-06-GAN/#з•ЮзїПзљСзїЬ" class="headerlink" title="Permalink to this headline">¬ґ</a>
</h2>

<p>ињЩйЗМдЉЪеИЫеїЇдЄ§дЄ™з•ЮзїПзљСзїЬ, еИЖеИЂжШѓ Generator (жЦ∞жЙЛзФїеЃґ), Discriminator(жЦ∞жЙЛйЙіиµПеЃґ).
<code class="highlighter-rouge">G</code> дЉЪжЛњзЭАиЗ™еЈ±зЪДдЄАдЇЫзБµжДЯељУеБЪиЊУеЕ•, иЊУеЗЇдЄАеЕГдЇМжђ°жЫ≤зЇњдЄКзЪДзВє (<code class="highlighter-rouge">G</code> зЪДзФї).</p>

<p><code class="highlighter-rouge">D</code> дЉЪжО•жФґдЄАеєЕзФїдљЬ (дЄАеЕГдЇМжђ°жЫ≤зЇњ), иЊУеЗЇињЩеєЕзФїдљЬеИ∞еЇХжШѓдЄНжШѓиСЧеРНзФїеЃґзЪДзФї(жШѓиСЧеРНзФїеЃґзЪДзФїзЪДж¶ВзОЗ).</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">G</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">nn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Sequential</span><span class="p">(</span>                      <span class="c1"># Generator
</span>    <span class="n">nn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Linear</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">N_IDEAS</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">128</span><span class="p">),</span>            <span class="c1"># random ideas (could from normal distribution)
</span>    <span class="n">nn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">ReLU</span><span class="p">(),</span>
    <span class="n">nn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Linear</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">128</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">ART_COMPONENTS</span><span class="p">),</span>     <span class="c1"># making a painting from these random ideas
</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="n">D</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">nn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Sequential</span><span class="p">(</span>                      <span class="c1"># Discriminator
</span>    <span class="n">nn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Linear</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">ART_COMPONENTS</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">128</span><span class="p">),</span>     <span class="c1"># receive art work either from the famous artist or a newbie like G
</span>    <span class="n">nn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">ReLU</span><span class="p">(),</span>
    <span class="n">nn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Linear</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">128</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">),</span>
    <span class="n">nn</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Sigmoid</span><span class="p">(),</span>                       <span class="c1"># tell the probability that the art work is made by artist
</span><span class="p">)</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

