<h2 class="tut-h2-pad" id="иЃ≠зїГ">иЃ≠зїГ
  <a href="/tutorials/machine-learning/torch/4-06-GAN/#иЃ≠зїГ" class="headerlink" title="Permalink to this headline">¬ґ</a>
</h2>

<p>жО•зЭАжИСдїђжЭ•еРМжЧґиЃ≠зїГ <code class="highlighter-rouge">D</code> еТМ <code class="highlighter-rouge">G</code>. иЃ≠зїГдєЛеЙН, жИСдїђжЭ•зЬЛзЬЛ<code class="highlighter-rouge">G</code>дљЬзФїзЪДеОЯзРЖ.
<code class="highlighter-rouge">G</code> й¶ЦеЕИдЉЪжЬЙдЇЫзБµжДЯ, <code class="highlighter-rouge">G_ideas</code> е∞±дЉЪжЛњеИ∞ињЩдЇЫйЪПжЬЇзБµжДЯ (еПѓдї•жШѓж≠£жАБеИЖеЄГзЪДйЪПжЬЇжХ∞), зДґеРО <code class="highlighter-rouge">G</code> дЉЪж†єжНЃињЩдЇЫзБµжДЯзФїзФї.
жО•зЭАжИСдїђжЛњзЭАиСЧеРНзФїеЃґзЪДзФїеТМ <code class="highlighter-rouge">G</code> зЪДзФї, иЃ© <code class="highlighter-rouge">D</code> жЭ•еИ§еЃЪињЩдЄ§жЙєзФїдљЬжШѓиСЧеРНзФїеЃґзФїзЪДж¶ВзОЗ.</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">step</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nb">range</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">10000</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="n">artist_paintings</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">artist_works</span><span class="p">()</span>           <span class="c1"># real painting from artist
</span>    <span class="n">G_ideas</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">torch</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">randn</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">BATCH_SIZE</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">N_IDEAS</span><span class="p">)</span>    <span class="c1"># random ideas
</span>    <span class="n">G_paintings</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">G</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">G_ideas</span><span class="p">())</span>                  <span class="c1"># fake painting from G (random ideas)
</span>
    <span class="n">prob_artist0</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">D</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">artist_paintings</span><span class="p">)</span>          <span class="c1"># D try to increase this prob
</span>    <span class="n">prob_artist1</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">D</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">G_paintings</span><span class="p">)</span>               <span class="c1"># D try to reduce this prob
</span></code></pre></div></div>

<p>зДґеРОиЃ°зЃЧжЬЙе§Ъе∞СжЭ•дєЛзФїеЃґзЪДзФїзМЬеѓєдЇЖ, жЬЙе§Ъе∞СжЭ•иЗ™ <code class="highlighter-rouge">G</code> зЪДзФїзМЬеѓєдЇЖ, жИСдїђжГ≥жЬАе§ІеМЦињЩдЇЫзМЬеѓєзЪДжђ°жХ∞.
ињЩдєЯе∞±жШѓ <code class="highlighter-rouge">log(D(x)) + log(1-D(G(z))</code> еЬ®<a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/1406.2661" target="_blank">иЃЇжЦЗ</a>дЄ≠зЪДељҐеЉП.
иАМеЫ†дЄЇ torch дЄ≠жПРеНЗеПВжХ∞зЪДељҐеЉПжШѓжЬАе∞ПеМЦиѓѓеЈЃ, йВ£жИСдїђжККжЬАе§ІеМЦ <code class="highlighter-rouge">score</code> иљђжНҐжИРжЬАе∞ПеМЦ <code class="highlighter-rouge">loss</code>, еЬ®дЄ§дЄ™ <code class="highlighter-rouge">score</code> зЪДеРИзЪДеЬ∞жЦєеК†дЄАдЄ™зђ¶еПЈе∞±е•љ.
